stock-compelling-valuation-steady-growth-improving-margins\">initial recommendation</a> in July, where I recognized the company's <a href=\"https://investor.daktronics.com/static-files/257100da-05a9-46a8-aabb-46a6b94ce736\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">leading position in the US market</a> with a promising outlook</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742308-daktronics-q2-digital-transformation-set-to-drive-strong-margin-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:30:03"}, {"id": "4741491", "title": "2 REITs To Buy Before December 18th", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"clock series\" data-id=\"157394764\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peepo/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed has already cut interest rates two times, and it is expected to cut rates again at the next meeting on December 18th.</p> <p></p> <p>This is very bullish for REITs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) because their market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741491-2-reits-to-buy-before-december-18th", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:25:00"}, {"id": "4742305", "title": "BNY Mellon Core Plus Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wooden cube block with Value business word and plus icon on blue background. Mission, Vision, and Core Values Concept\" data-id=\"1691340619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Userba011d64_201/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>\u201cWe expect economic growth in most developed economies to moderate to sub-trend levels, while inflation gradually eases back to target levels. Monetary policy easing is set to continue through the final quarter of the year and into</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742305-bny-mellon-core-plus-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:18:00"}, {"id": "4742304", "title": "Roku's Takeover Rumor And How It Impacts Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wealthy Entrepreneur\" data-id=\"157444694\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RichVintage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Recently, American technology company Roku (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ROKU\" title=\"Roku, Inc.\">ROKU</a></span>) has been the subject of equity research reports by a handful of sell-side equity research firms that have issued multiple reports expecting the San Jose, CA-based streaming device maker to be</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742304-rokus-takeover-rumor-and-how-it-impacts-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:15:41"}, {"id": "4742318", "title": "NAV Monitor: U.S. Equity REITs End November At 6.5% Median Discount", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate concept business, home insurance and real estate protection. Real estate investment concept. Buy and sell houses and real estate online on a virtual screen.\" data-id=\"2154752387\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">phakphum patjangkata</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Publicly listed US equity real estate investment trusts closed Nov. 29 at a median 6.5% discount to their consensus net asset value per share estimates, 2.8 percentage points down from a median discount of 9.3% as of Nov. 1, according to S&amp;P Global Market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742318-nav-monitor-us-equity-reits-end-november-at-6-5-percent-median-discount", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:10:00"}, {"id": "4741877", "title": "Rare Stock Picks In November 2024 - From 28 Discerning Analysts", "description": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/3/saupload_needle_in_haystack.png\" vspace=\"6\" hspace=\"6\" alt=\"\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\">November turned out to be yet another buy the dip opportunity. Even with the SPY up ~27% YTD, are there any compelling investment ideas out there that may have flown under your radar?</p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\">Below is a list of November Buy recommendations made by analysts who had no other bullish recommendations over the past 3 months.</p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\">For your directory assistance, we've classified the opportunities by sector.</p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/3/saupload_alpha_image.png\" vspace=\"6\" hspace=\"6\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p> <h2>Healthcare</h2> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Moberg Pharma</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MBGPF\" title=\"Moberg Pharma AB (publ)\">OTCPK:MBGPF</a>) - Longtime analyst <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/michigan-value-investor/analysis\">Michigan Value Investor</a> highlights this under the radar idea with a strong balance sheet and strong earnings power, driven by its toenail fungus treatment, which immediately moved to a 40% market share in Sweden with a broader EU launch set for Q1 2026. - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4737575-consider-buying-moberg-pharma-ahead-of-drug-launch\">Consider Buying Moberg Pharma Ahead Of Drug Launch</a></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Medpace</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MEDP\" title=\"Medpace Holdings, Inc.\">MEDP</a>) - Individual investor <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/paul-dutz/analysis\">Paul Dutz</a> says that although short-term headwinds have impacted the stock, its robust operational outlook and potential for continued growth makes it a compelling investment. - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732083-medpace-a-compelling-long-term-opportunity-amid-short-term-headwinds\">Medpace: A Compelling Long-Term Opportunity Amid Short-Term Headwinds (Rating Upgrade)</a></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Pfizer</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PFE\" title=\"Pfizer Inc.\">PFE</a>) - Dividend growth investor <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/dividendrodeo/analysis\">DividendRodeo</a> says the high initial dividend yield, solid ratings, and promising pipeline make it a potentially undervalued investment. - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740601-high-quality-dividend-growth-stocks-near-52-week-lows-pfizer-is-fun\">High-Quality Dividend Growth Stocks Near 52-Week Lows: Pfizer Is Fun</a></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/3/saupload_alpha_image_1.png\" vspace=\"6\" hspace=\"6\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p> <h2>Financials</h2> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Adams Natural Resources Fund</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PEO\" title=\"Adams Natural Resources Fund, Inc.\">PEO</a>) - Longtime analyst <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/gv-strategies/analysis\">GV Strategies</a> says it trades at a discount to NAV, with potential for tightening due to improved distribution policies and activist investor involvement. - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724150-peo-buy-dip-in-this-resources-fund-before-oil-rises\">PEO: Buy The Dip In This Resources Fund Before The Oil Price Rises</a> (<em>Editor\u2019s note: this article was originally published in late September</em>)</p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>StoneCo</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STNE\" title=\"StoneCo Ltd.\">STNE</a>) - Longtime analyst <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/roman-vitasek/analysis\">Roman Vitasek, CFA</a> says the decline after earnings (attributed to macroeconomic headwinds and market-driven factors) presents a potential buying opportunity as it trades at a significant discount to intrinsic value, offering substantial upside potential with limited downside risk for</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741877-rare-stock-picks-in-november-2024-from-28-discerning-analysts", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4742313", "title": "Coking Coal's Rollercoaster Ride: What 2024 Taught Us About Steelmaking's Essential Ingredient", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"piles of coking coal\" data-id=\"182913202\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4300px\" height=\"2823px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182913202/image_182913202.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">shank_ali</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><a href=\"https://agmetalminer.com/2024/12/03/coking-coals-rollercoaster-ride/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Original Post</em></a></p> <p><em>By Sohrab Darabshaw</em></p> <p>The story of coking coal in 2024, especially its price in global markets, has mainly been \"one step forward and one step